Class IdentityProjection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.platform.location.core.geospatial.IdentityProjection

  • public class IdentityProjection
extends java.lang.Object
    A debugging GeoProjection.

    This projection does not apply any transformation. The longitude values is used as the x value and the latitude value is used as the y.
